Output demo.gif

Set Shell bash
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20

Set TypingSpeed 100ms
Type "ppd"
Sleep 600ms
Hide
Ctrl+U
Type "npm start"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show

Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Type "Hello world! "
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Type "This is promptpad "
Sleep 300ms
Set TypingSpeed 120ms
Type "- a minimal terminal text editor."
Sleep 1s

Enter
Enter
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Type "It tracks lines, characters, and tokens."
Sleep 1s
